        {
            "title": "思格新能首掛高收1.03倍 每手賬賺3.35萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">思格新能(06656)挾著IPO在港售股超購1101倍之勢，今日掛牌表現未負眾望，高收1.03倍，以659.5元收市。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"思格新能源於香港交易所主板掛牌上市\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/600x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/temp_a8ea11e4_02.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"思格新能源於香港交易所主板掛牌上市\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/600x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/temp_a8ea11e4_02.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">思格新能源於香港交易所主板掛牌上市</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以該股1手100股計，認購並獲配每手賬面賺3.35萬元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股今早於競價時段高開79.21%，以581元開市，日中低位560.5元時仍較招股價324.2元高72.89%；午後動力提升，尾市前曾衝上669元，高於招股價1.06倍。單日成交45.97億元</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15881155-%e6%80%9d%e6%a0%bc%e6%96%b0%e8%83%bd%e9%a6%96%e6%8e%9b%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b61-03%e5%80%8d-%e6%af%8f%e6%89%8b%e8%b3%ac%e8%b3%ba3-35%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/06656.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 16:24:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市︱午後再揚 恒指升446點報26394點 科股領風騷 壁仞科技、天數智芯齊爆發",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股午後再上層樓，一舉收復兩萬六、以及50天與100天線。重磅科股固然是升市功臣，壁仞科技(06082)等新興科技領域的成員亦爆發。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"壁仞科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/Biren.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"壁仞科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/Biren.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">壁仞科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早高開175點、報26122點即成全日低位，重越26000點、50天線(最新約為26038點)、100天線(最新約為26078點)，其後升幅反覆擴大，午後最高曾見26403點，漲455點，午市幾乎全程在26300點之上徘徊。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指最後收報26394點，升446點或1.72%。恒生科技指數明顯跑贏，收升180點或3.67%，報5092點；國企指數升186點或2.14%，報8905點。主板成交2562.28億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15881146-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%86%8d%e6%8f%9a-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87446%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126394%e9%bb%9e-%e7%a7%91%e8%82%a1%e9%a0%98%e9%a2%a8%e9%a8%b7-%e5%a3%81",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-5.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 16:14:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股午後升幅擴大  深股收升逾2%  兩市成交逾23400億人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股午後升破上午高位，深股升幅擴大至超過2%，創業板指數收升逾3%，兩市成交合計23416.78億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-15.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-15.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指全日報4055，升28點或0.7%，今早以4030點開市，升2點或0.07%，早段見4028點，升1點，為全日低位，三頭馬車數據公布，大市向上，午後升破上午低位，見4057，升30點或0.74%，為全日高位。全日成交 9765.65億元</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指全日報14796，升297點或2.05%，今早開市報14546點，亦升47點或0.33%。早段見14522，跌24點或0.17%，為全日低位，午後高見14807，升309點或2.13%，為全日高位，半日成交13651.13億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數收報4736，升51點或1.1%，今早開升9點或0.2%，開報4694點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數全日報3626點，升111點或3.17%，今早開市報3531點，升16點或0.46%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15880579-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be2-%e5%85%a9%e5%b8%82%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4%e9%80%be23400%e5%84%84%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-14.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 15:09:18",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
